{"id":"triangles","body":"\n\n<div class=\"bubble-objectives\">\n<ul>\n<li><p>Construire des triangles.</p></li>\n<li><p>Connaître et utiliser les propriétés angulaires des triangles\nparticuliers : rectangle, isocèle, équilatéral.</p></li>\n<li><p>Connaître la valeur de la somme des mesures des angles d’un\ntriangle.</p></li>\n<li><p>Utiliser cette somme pour calculer des angles, effectuer des\nconstructions et résoudre des problèmes.</p></li>\n<li><p>Savoir que les médiatrices d’un triangle sont\nconcourantes.</p></li>\n<li><p>Connaître et construire le cercle circonscrit à un\ntriangle.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2>Rappels</h2>\n<h3>Définitions</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-remember\">\n<h4>Définitions</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Un <strong>triangle</strong> est un polygone à trois\ncôtés.</p></li>\n<li><p>Un <strong>triangle rectangle</strong> est un triangle qui a un\nangle droit.</p></li>\n<li><p>Un <strong>triangle isocèle</strong> est un triangle qui a deux\ncôtés de même longueur.</p></li>\n<li><p>Un <strong>triangle équilatéral</strong> est un triangle qui a\ntrois côtés de même longueur.</p></li>\n<li><p>Un <strong>triangle quelconque</strong> est un triangle qui n’est\nni rectangle, ni isocèle, ni équilatéral.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Parmi les triangles ci-dessous, entourer :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>en rouge le triangle rectangle ;</p></li>\n<li><p>en bleu le triangle isocèle ;</p></li>\n<li><p>en vert le triangle équilatéral ;</p></li>\n<li><p>en noir le triangle quelconque.</p></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-1.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-1\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-2.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-2\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h3>Construction</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-remember\">\n<h4>Propriété</h4>\n<p>On peut construire un triangle si et seulement si :</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p><span id=\"cas-1\" data-label=\"cas-1\"></span> on connaît les\nlongueurs des trois côtés du triangle ;</p></li>\n<li><p><span id=\"cas-2\" data-label=\"cas-2\"></span> on connaît la\nlongueur de deux côtés et la mesure de l’angle formé par ces deux côtés\n;</p></li>\n<li><p><span id=\"cas-3\" data-label=\"cas-3\"></span> on connaît la mesure\nde deux angles et la longueur du côté commun à ces deux angles.</p></li>\n</ol>\n<p>On peut utiliser la règle et le compas dans le cas <a href=\"#cas-1\"\ndata-reference-type=\"ref\" data-reference=\"cas-1\">[cas-1]</a> et la règle\net le rapporteur dans les cas <a href=\"#cas-2\" data-reference-type=\"ref\"\ndata-reference=\"cas-2\">[cas-2]</a> et <a href=\"#cas-3\"\ndata-reference-type=\"ref\" data-reference=\"cas-3\">[cas-3]</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Construire le triangle <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">XM</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span></span></span></span> tel que <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">XM</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span></span></span></span> cm, <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">M</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span></span></span></span> cm et <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">X</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span> cm.</p>\n<div class=\"vertical-space\" style=\"height: 4.1cm;\"></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-3.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-3\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Construire le triangle <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">EB</span></span></span></span> tel que <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">E</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span></span></span></span> cm, <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">5</span></span></span></span> cm et <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">E</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">W</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span></span></span><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.6833em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span style=\"height:0.3em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"0.3em\" viewBox=\"0 0 2364 300\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M1181 0h2l1171 176c6 0 10 5 10 11l-2 23c-1 6-5 10\n-11 10h-1L1182 67 15 220h-1c-6 0-10-4-11-10l-2-23c-1-6 4-11 10-11z\"></path></svg></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">40</span></span></span></span>°.</p>\n<div class=\"vertical-space\" style=\"height: 4.1cm;\"></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-4.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-4\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Construire le triangle <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span></span></span></span> tel que <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">5</span></span></span></span> cm, <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">UL</span></span></span><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.6833em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span style=\"height:0.3em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"0.3em\" viewBox=\"0 0 2364 300\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M1181 0h2l1171 176c6 0 10 5 10 11l-2 23c-1 6-5 10\n-11 10h-1L1182 67 15 220h-1c-6 0-10-4-11-10l-2-23c-1-6 4-11 10-11z\"></path></svg></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">25</span></span></span></span>° et\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.00773em;\">R</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">U</span></span></span><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.6833em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span style=\"height:0.3em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"0.3em\" viewBox=\"0 0 2364 300\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M1181 0h2l1171 176c6 0 10 5 10 11l-2 23c-1 6-5 10\n-11 10h-1L1182 67 15 220h-1c-6 0-10-4-11-10l-2-23c-1-6 4-11 10-11z\"></path></svg></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">34</span></span></span></span>°.</p>\n<div class=\"vertical-space\" style=\"height: 4.1cm;\"></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-5.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-5\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h3>Hauteur issue d’un sommet</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-remember\">\n<h4>Définition</h4>\n<p>Soit <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">BC</span></span></span></span> un triangle. La <strong>hauteur</strong>\ndu triangle <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">BC</span></span></span></span> issue de <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span> est\nla droite passant par le point <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span> et perpendiculaire\nà la droite <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">BC</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Dans les deux triangles <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">BC</span></span></span></span> ci-dessous, avec\nl’équerre, tracer la hauteur du triangle <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">BC</span></span></span></span> issue\nde <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span>. Appeler <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">h</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> cette hauteur\net <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07847em;\">I</span></span></span></span> le point d’intersection entre <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">h</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> et <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">BC</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>.</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-6.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-6\"></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-7.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-7\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-8.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-8\"></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-9.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-9\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h2>Propriétés</h2>\n<h3>Médiatrices</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-remember\">\n<h4>Définition</h4>\n<p>La <strong>médiatrice</strong> d’un segment est la droite\nperpendiculaire à celui-ci qui passe par son milieu.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-remember\">\n<h4>Propriété</h4>\n<p>Les trois médiatrices des côtés d’un triangle se coupent en un point\n: il s’agit du centre du <strong>cercle circonscrit</strong> au\ntriangle. Celui-ci passe par tous les sommets du triangle.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Tracer les trois médiatrices du triangle <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span>\nci-dessous. Puis, tracer le cercle circonscrit à <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">L</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span>.</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-10.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-10\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/triangles-cours/tikzpicture-11.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-11\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h3>Somme des angles</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-remember\">\n<h4>Propriété</h4>\n<p>Dans un triangle, la somme des mesures des angles est de <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">180</span></span></span></span>°.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-remember\">\n<h4>Corollaires</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><p>Les angles d’un triangle équilatéral mesurent <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">60</span></span></span></span>°.</p></li>\n<li><p>Les angles de la base d’un triangle isocèle ont la même\nmesure.</p></li>\n<li><p>La somme des angles aigus d’un triangle rectangle vaut <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">90</span></span></span></span>°.</p></li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercise\">\n\n<p>Soit <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">BC</span></span></span></span> un triangle isocèle en <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span> tel que <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.6833em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span style=\"height:0.3em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"0.3em\" viewBox=\"0 0 2364 300\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M1181 0h2l1171 176c6 0 10 5 10 11l-2 23c-1 6-5 10\n-11 10h-1L1182 67 15 220h-1c-6 0-10-4-11-10l-2-23c-1-6 4-11 10-11z\"></path></svg></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">40</span></span></span></span>°.\nMontrer que <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.9833em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">CB</span></span></span><span class=\"svg-align\" style=\"top:-3.6833em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span style=\"height:0.3em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"0.3em\" viewBox=\"0 0 2364 300\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><path d=\"M1181 0h2l1171 176c6 0 10 5 10 11l-2 23c-1 6-5 10\n-11 10h-1L1182 67 15 220h-1c-6 0-10-4-11-10l-2-23c-1-6 4-11 10-11z\"><